      "span_text": "In addition, the seed was anatomically restricted to the SPL according to the Automated Anatomical Labeling atlas. Based on these criteria, time series were extracted from two 6 mm seeds, one placed in left SPL (MNI coordinates: -18 -63 54) and one in right SPL (MNI coordinates: 27 -63 51)."
